@startuml
title Digital Therapy Assistant - System Context

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 12
}

actor Patient
actor Therapist
actor Administrator

rectangle "Digital Therapy Assistant" as DTA
rectangle "LLM Provider" as LLM
rectangle "Email Service" as EMAIL
rectangle "EHR Systems" as EHR

Patient --> DTA : uses CBT support,\ndiary, progress, and crisis tools
Therapist --> DTA : reviews support data\nand patient outcomes
Administrator --> DTA : manages operations\nand configuration
DTA --> LLM : requests analysis\nand generated responses
DTA --> EMAIL : sends notifications\nand support messages
DTA --> EHR : exchanges care context\nand outcome data

@enduml
